us on new technologies. Lucid, compelling and rigorously researched, this book will have a lasting impact on how we think about climate change.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aSCIENCE / Environmental Science (see also Chemistry / Environmental).2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030018864640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300188646423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300188646/original  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY